snippet.title: Rivals 2 Fleet Character Reveal Trailer
snippet.description: Fleet's on to her next adventure as she officially joins the cast of Rivals 2! Voiced by Faye Mata, the Archer of Justice snipes, snacks, and sails through the air in battle. Rivals 2 is now available to wishlist on Steam! Help show your support by heading to https://rivals2.com/wishlist
